Media.


Features:

- fetch new releases (scene releases, tv schedule, music reviews)
- grab new media matching filters (rating, genre, date...)
- grab similar media (directors movies, similar bands albums)
- grab movies and tv shows subtitles
- unpack, clean and sort new media into the media type based directories
- fetch media metadata (director, release date, etc)
- retrieve media trailers and audio tracks
- sync media to network hosts (e.g.: phones)


Start the worker:
./media/run.py
